<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    .container {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .content {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">Hello, <%= username %>!</div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Welcome to our service. We are excited to have you!</p>
      <p>Let us know if you need any assistance.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
